quran[11{c,v,t}:
27,45,"aur smod ki taraf hum ne unn ke bhai Saleh ko ( yeh pegham day kar ) bheja ke Allah ki bandagi karo, to yakayak woh do mutakhasim fareeq (jhagarnay walay) ban gay"
27,46,"saleh ne kaha"" “ay meri qoum ke logo, bhalai se pehlay buraii ke liye kyun jaldi machate ho? kyun nahi Allah se mughfirat talab karte? shayad ke tum par reham farmaya jaye? """
27,47,"unhon ne kaha"" hum ne to tum ko aur tumahray sathiyon ko bad shugooni ka nishaan paaya hai"" saleh ne jawab diya"" “tumharay naik o bad shagoon ka sir rishta to Allah ke paas hai asal baat yeh hai ke tum logon ki azmaish ho rahi hai """
27,48,uss shehar mein no jithay daar thay jo malik mein fasaad pheilatay aur koi islaah ka kaam nah karte thay
27,49,"unhon ne aapas mein kaha"" khuda ki qasam kha kar ehad kar lau ke hum saleh aur is ke ghar walon par shab khoon marain ge aur phir is ke walii se keh den ge ke hum is khandan ki halakat ke mauqa par mojood nah thay, hum bilkul sach kehte hain """
27,50,yeh chaal to woh chalay aur phir aik chaal hum ne chali jis ki inhen khabar nah thi
27,51,ab dekh lau ke un ki chaal ka injaam kya howa hum ne tabah kar ke rakh diya unn ko aur un ki poori qoum ko
27,52,"woh unn ke ghar khaali parre hain uss zulm ki Padaash mein jo woh karte thay, is mein aik nishaan Ibrat hai unn logon ke liye jo ilm rakhtay hain"
27,53,aur bacha liya hum ne unn logon ko jo imaan laaye thay aur nafarmani se parhaiz karte thay
27,54,"aur loot ko hum ne bheja yaad karo woh waqt jab is ne apni qoum se kaha"" kya tum aankhon dekhte badkaari karte ho ?"
27,55,"kya tumhara yahi chalan hai ke aurton ko chore kar mardon ke paas shehwat rani ke liye jatay ho? haqeeqat yeh hai ke tum log sakht jahalat ka kaam karte ho """
